00:35:02.344 --> 00:35:05.824
So sensitivity at 50%. That's not really good.

615
00:35:06.304 --> 00:35:08.184
According to what I've been telling you all along, it's not very good.

616
00:35:08.584 --> 00:35:11.824
However, that's not the clinical use for this assay here.

617
00:35:11.864 --> 00:35:15.203
It's a monitoring assay. So if you can actually identify those patients, you can

